{"tid":326800,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"搵到工等返工既日子好撚頹","createTime":"2017-07-18T09:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T12:34:16.000Z","uid":43276,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"311097aea3f8fe3286bfa6e0ff425089f23674b3","tid":326800,"uid":43276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:29:05.000Z","msg":"幾經辛苦千山萬水排除萬難用盡畢生運氣先搵到工果下真係好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但仲有一個月先返工而家空窗期唔知做乜好<br />\n其實想趁返工前去個小旅行 但又無決心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日係屋企鳩下鳩下唔知做乜 呢排又成撚日落雨搞到連出街買個麥記食下都費時<br />\n又毒又無人約 我約人又無人理我<br />\n有無巴絲都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵工時都話有啲目的 而家真心頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ca3389b8e063b2475efe39b004b4f596dd3909","tid":326800,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:31:04.000Z","msg":"一柒樣，利申：膠up"},{"pid":"18a839abfee91737242b0155664f160d6f341aa9","tid":326800,"uid":43276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:32:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一柒樣，利申：膠up</blockquote><br />\n巴打幾時返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4014913ddc4e312c336bbec1ecdbfb11e74060a0","tid":326800,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:35:59.000Z","msg":"去旅行都要決心 你都係跳樓死撚左佢算啦廢柴"},{"pid":"c7507040229f28c011218cdb43466cb0089054bc","tid":326800,"uid":43276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:38:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去旅行都要決心 你都係跳樓死撚左佢算啦廢柴</blockquote><br />\n買機票那一刻就是決心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef7532768680353c613a9ea17995f337e6a5fe0","tid":326800,"uid":78604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:44:37.000Z","msg":"一樣<br />\n八月一返工 宜家日日五點先起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"